" Mini-Ranch ", JUST REDUCED Nicely Maintained and has a very OPEN FLOOR PLAN.
2020 NEW ROOF, 2020 NEW REFRIGERATOR,2020 DISHWASHER,2020 WATER HEATER.
HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED,12 MONTHS.
GREAT AFFORDABLE PROPERTY FOR FAMILY, INVESTMENT, OR GETAWAY HOME.  
“MINI-RANCH”  total 2.2 acres WITH 1/3rd of the property Pipe & Cable Fencing of COMBO BARN,LOFTING SHED, AND CONTAINER WITHIN THE WORKING CORRAL AREA. Unique Other 2/3rd of property for Residential including Privacy fenced area for Fur Babies area off back deck, with In ground Concrete Storm shelter.
Note: 12-10-2023 Contract with Contingency in hand so far.
MUST SEE. Popular Okarche Schools. Semi rare Over 2 acres property in Okarche. Just 16 miles NW of OKC Line!
